facts_en:
On February 10, 2021, at approximately 22:50, in front of Building C of Apartment Complex B, upon receiving a 112 emergency report raising suspicion that the defendant was operating a motor vehicle while under the influence of alcohol, police officers—Sergeant E and Police Corporal F, both assigned to D Police Station—arrived at the scene and requested that the defendant submit to a breathalyzer test. The defendant refused to comply with this request.

When Sergeant E and Police Corporal F informed the defendant to the effect that "despite the police officer's lawful request for an alcohol breath test, the defendant unreasonably delayed and committed a first refusal to submit to an alcohol breath test, and should the defendant refuse again, such conduct would constitute a second refusal to submit to an alcohol breath test," the defendant became angry and directed vulgar profanity at Sergeant E and Police Corporal F, stating "You motherfucking bastards," while attempting to leave the scene.

When Sergeant E attempted to restrain the defendant, the defendant committed assault as follows:

- pushed Sergeant E's chest area three times with his hands;
- kicked Sergeant E's leg with his foot;
- bit Sergeant E's right hand with his teeth;
- pushed Police Corporal F's body with his hands as the latter approached the defendant;
- kicked Police Corporal F's laryngeal region with his foot after Police Corporal F bent down in response to the defendant's request to loosen the handcuffs that had been applied to the arrested defendant.

By committing the aforementioned acts of assault, the defendant obstructed the police officers' lawful execution of their official duties in processing the 112 emergency report and conducting enforcement operations against drunk driving.

## Prior Criminal History

The defendant was sentenced as follows:

- March 24, 1999, at the District Court: Fraud (징역죄), 8 months imprisonment and 2 years suspended sentence;
- December 24, 2003, at the District Court: Fraud, 6 months imprisonment;
- August 16, 2004, at the District Court: Fraud, 8 months imprisonment;
- November 24, 2005, at the District Court: Fraud, 10 months imprisonment;
- February 10, 2006, at the District Court: Fraud, 10 months imprisonment;
- November 17, 2006, at the District Court: Fraud, 9 months imprisonment;
- November 1, 2007, at the District Court: Habitual Fraud, 10 months imprisonment;
- December 18, 2008, at the District Court: Fraud, 1 year 2 months imprisonment;
- July 29, 2010, at the District Court: Fraud, 10 months imprisonment;
- May 26, 2011, at the District Court: Fraud, 10 months imprisonment; this judgment became final on October 19, 2011, and the defendant completed execution of the sentence on January 26, 2012, while imprisoned;
- January 11, 2013, at the District Court: Fraud and others, 10 months imprisonment and a fine of 3,000,000 won; the defendant was released on May 23, 2013, following cancellation of detention.

In addition to the foregoing, the defendant has 13 further prior convictions for similar offenses.



## Case No. 2013고단3783

On November 11, 2013, at approximately 19:10, the defendant visited "D Noraebang Bar" operated by Victim C. Despite the fact that the defendant lacked both the intent and the ability to pay for alcoholic beverages and other items provided by the victim, the defendant stated, "Don't worry about the bar tab; I will pay however much is needed," thereby acting as if he would normally pay for the alcoholic beverages. By deceiving the victim in this manner, the defendant received from the victim property valued at a total of 430,000 won, consisting of 30 bottles of beer, 5 side dishes (안주), and karaoke room usage service (7 hours), thereby obtaining property through fraud and deception of the victim.



## Case No. 2014고단1798

On March 1, 2014, at approximately 03:00, the defendant visited the "Party Party" bar operated by Victim Kwon O.O. Despite the fact that the defendant lacked both the intent and the ability to pay normally for alcoholic beverages and other items provided by the victim, the defendant acted as if he would normally pay for the alcoholic beverages and ordered from the victim 2 bottles of spirits, 1 bottle of beer, and side dishes valued at 39,000 won in total. By deceiving the victim, the defendant received the ordered items from the victim and thereby acquired economic or financial benefit (재산상 이익) equivalent to that amount.



## Case No. 2014고단1849

On June 11, 2014, at approximately 23:30, the defendant visited the "Casting" noraebang bar operated by Victim Lee O.O. Despite the fact that the defendant lacked both the intent and the ability to pay normally for alcoholic beverages and other items provided by the victim, the defendant acted as if he would normally pay for the alcoholic beverages and ordered from the victim 2 bottles of spirits, beer, and side dishes valued at 500,000 won in total. By deceiving the victim, the defendant received the ordered items from the victim and thereby acquired economic or financial benefit equivalent to that amount.

The defendant and Victim B were inmates housed together in the Closed Ward C of the correctional facility. The defendant harbored a grievance against Victim B, finding the victim's movements slow and speech somewhat unclear, which the defendant found frustrating.

Accordingly, the defendant:

1) On approximately January 1, 2021 at 08:00, in the aforementioned Closed Ward C of the correctional facility, kicked Victim B once on the side of the ribs and once on the chest with the defendant's foot, on the pretext that the victim had soiled the dining table with food during a meal;

2) On approximately January 5, 2021 at 07:30, in the aforementioned location, kicked Victim B two to three times on both sides of the ribs with the defendant's foot and struck both cheeks of the victim twice with the defendant's left hand, on the pretext that the victim had not prepared for inspection;

3) On approximately January 8, 2021 at 15:00, in the aforementioned location, kicked Victim B once on the right side of the ribs with the defendant's left foot, on the pretext that the victim had taken an inordinate amount of time in the bathroom;

4) On approximately January 9, 2021 at 17:00, in the aforementioned location, struck Victim B once on the chest with the defendant's left fist and struck the victim once on the left side of the face with the back of the defendant's left hand, on the pretext that the victim had set the dining table with unwashed hands that had touched a cleaning rag;

5) On approximately January 11, 2021 at 12:00, in the aforementioned location, kicked Victim B three times on the chest with the defendant's left foot on the pretext that the victim had not corrected their habits, and subsequently on the same day at approximately 14:00, struck the victim once on the left side of the ribs with the defendant's left fist;

6) On approximately January 13, 2021 at 08:00, in the aforementioned location, struck Victim B twice on the face with the defendant's left hand, on the pretext that the victim had lied about not having swept water on the bathroom floor.

By these acts, the defendant inflicted upon Victim B injuries requiring approximately six weeks of treatment, including multiple rib fractures, traumatic hemothorax without open wound into the pleural cavity, and contusions of the eyelids and periocular region.

The defendant was in a common-law relationship with Victim B. Victim C is the wife of Victim B.

**Factual Background:**
On July 10, 2020, at approximately 20:40, the defendant went to Building E located in D, where the victims resided, for the reason that Victim B had refused to meet with the defendant.

## 1. ASSAULT AGAINST VICTIM C

On the aforementioned date and time, in the parking lot of Building E, while engaged in a verbal altercation with the victim, the defendant heard the victim say, "You lived in poverty until your mother died and you became a sudden windfall heir, didn't you? Looking at your face makes me want to vomit." Enraged by this remark, the defendant:

- struck the victim's face once with his right elbow;
- grabbed the victim's hair and struck her face once with his hand;
- kicked the victim's lower body once with his foot;
- grabbed the victim's hair with his hand and threw her to the ground; and
- stepped on the victim's torso once with his foot while she lay on the ground.

**Injury Sustained:** The defendant thereby inflicted injuries upon the victim, including cervical, thoracic, and lumbar sprain, requiring approximately 14 days of medical treatment.



## 2. ASSAULT AGAINST VICTIM B

On the aforementioned date and time, at the aforementioned location, while attempting to stop the defendant from striking Victim C as described in Count 1, the defendant:

- struck the victim's cheeks multiple times with his hand;
- struck the victim's head four times with a mobile phone;
- pushed the victim's neck twice with his hands;
- grabbed and dragged the victim's hair with both hands;
- struck the victim's face twice with both fists; and
- struck the victim's right facial area once with his right arm.

**Injury Sustained:** The defendant thereby inflicted injuries upon the victim, including left temporomandibular joint sprain, requiring approximately 14 days of medical treatment.

## CASE NUMBER: 2020고단3528

On June 17, 2020, at approximately 16:32, the Defendant engaged in a verbal altercation with Victim C on a street in front of B Villa regarding an automobile driving matter. During this altercation, the Defendant committed the following acts of violence:

1. Pushed Victim C's upper body once using his shoulder and abdomen;
2. Grabbed and pulled Victim C's neck from behind with his hand;
3. Struck Victim C's face with his head once;
4. Wrapped both hands around Victim C's neck and pulled;
5. Pushed Victim C's chest and neck areas multiple times with his hand.

Subsequently, on the same date at approximately 16:35, the Defendant engaged in a renewed verbal altercation with the Victim on a street in front of [location] D in the same district. During this second altercation, the Defendant committed the following acts:

1. Struck Victim C's face once with an open palm;
2. Struck Victim C's face once with a closed fist;
3. Kicked Victim C's left thigh once with his foot.

As a result of these assaults, the Defendant inflicted the following injuries upon Victim C: concussion requiring approximately two weeks of medical treatment; dental concussion (tooth luxation) requiring approximately ten days of medical treatment; and other bodily injuries.



## CASE NUMBER: 2021고단1942

On September 12, 2020, at approximately 03:50, the Defendant, angered by the fact that Victim G was speaking loudly on a telephone and smoking cigarettes, assaulted Victim G at an outdoor table in front of F' located at [venue] E. The Defendant committed the following acts of violence:

1. Struck Victim G's face with his fist approximately four times;
2. Knocked Victim G to the ground.

As a result of these assaults, the Defendant inflicted the following injury upon Victim G: lumbar strain (lower back sprain) requiring approximately fourteen days of medical treatment, and other bodily injuries.
